=300&amp;h=192&amp;crop=1"/></picture></a></div></div><div class="rail__item-content"><span class="rail__item-sub"><h3 class="rail__item-headline t-p-color">&#x27;CRUEL AND EVIL&#x27;</h3>Couple &#x27;gave kids meth &amp; shocked them with cattle prods for years&#x27;</span></div><div class="rail__item-cutoff"></div><a href="/news/11801991/couple-kids-methamphetamine-shocked-cattle-prods-years-abuse/" class="rail__item-anchor"></a></div></div><div class="swiper-pagination theme__swiper-pagination"></div><div class="swiper-button-prev theme__background-color-rgba-80"></div><div class="swiper-button-next theme__background-color-rgba-80"></div></div></div></div></div>
<p>The multinational drink and brewing company is based in Belgium, but have offices around the world, including in London and New York.</p>
<p>It produces the Corona brand as well as Budweiser and Stella Artois.</p>
<p>Corona is the third most popular beer in the US behind Guinness and Heineken, according to rankings by the market research company YouGov.</p>
